IB/rdmavt: Add common LID defines to rdmavt

Original patch is from Kamal Heib <kamalh@mellanox.com>. It has
been split into separate patches.

This patch adds RVT_PERMISSIVE_LID and RVT_MULTICAST_LID_BASE
to rdmavt.

